<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id5b69bb3c-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c" identifier="/us/usc/t29/s2636"><num value="2636">§ 2636.</num><heading> Termination</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Commission shall terminate 30 days after the date of the submission of the report of the Commission to Congress.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id5b69bb3d-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c">(<ref href="/us/pl/103/3/tIII/s306">Pub. L. 103–3, title III, § 306</ref>, <date date="1993-02-05">Feb. 5, 1993</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/107/25">107 Stat. 25</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
